Classes in twcore.core.events used by twcore.bots
ArenaJoined
          (S2C 0x02) Event called when a bot enters the arena.
ArenaList
           
BallPosition
          (S2C 0x2E) Event fired when a player picks up a ball.
FileArrived
          (S2C 0x10) Event called when the bot finishes the download of a file.
FlagClaimed
          (S2C 0x13) Event called when a player picks up or runs over a flag.
FlagDropped
          (S2C 0x16) Event called when a player drops a flag they are carrying.
FlagPosition
          (S2C 0x12) Event called when a flag is dropped, reset, or otherwise put somewhere else on the map.
FlagReward
          (S2C 0x23) Event called when a team gets periodic flag points from holding them.
FlagVictory
          (S2C 0x14) Event called when a team wins a flag jackpot.
FrequencyChange
          (S2C 0x0D) Event fired when a player changes frequencies.
FrequencyShipChange
          (S2C 0x1D) Event called when player changes ship (and possibly frequency) +------------------------------+ | Offset Length Description | +------------------------------+ | 0 1 Type Byte | | 1 1 Ship Type | | 2 2 Player ID | | 4 2 Frequency | +------------------------------+ Since this is the only packet associated with ship changing, getting this doesn't necessarily mean that they changed frequency too.
InterProcessEvent
          Event class of the Inter-process Communication protocol of TWCore.

          (S2C 0x04) Event is fired when a player leaves an arena.
